        <p class="para1">Standing poses do the most to strengthen your legs. While the focus is on your legs, these poses also incorporate the rest of your body. Yoga poses for leg strength include:</p>
        <ul class="list">
            <li>
                <strong>Beginner:</strong> Downward facing dog, Extended side angle pose
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Intermediate:</strong> Eagle pose
            </li>
